A motorcyclist has died in a collision with a car at a T-junction.Police were called shortly after 11:30 BST to the junction of Heath House Lane and Barnfield Way in Hedge End, Hampshire.The rider of a Triumph motorcycle, a man in his 20s, was pronounced dead at the scene.Officers have appealed for witnesses and dashcam footage of the bike or the Vauxhall car involved.
